{"tid":1674414,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"陳同佳其實係好男仔","createTime":"2019-10-25T07:56:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-25T12:24:12.000Z","uid":1734,"like":4,"dislike":14,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"3c436df772a233423fefe0b2c4aaafe3ccffb6cd","tid":1674414,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:56:18.000Z","msg":"佳佳生得型 身材又好 <br />\n屋企又錫佢 中學讀得開心 <br />\n竟然同個mk妹拍拖<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n放棄打機時間 都陪潘曉穎周圍玩<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/peanut.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去旅行又全程照顧佢<br />\n仲要當正佢係老婆<br />\n喺香港又同佢一齊住<br />\n佳佳仲要唔介意潘臭雞生得咁淫賤<br />\n唔介意佢係mk妹 以前比人屌過唔係處女<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本來佳佳有大好前途<br />\n未來十年可能係大商家<br />\n甚至可以做首富<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n如果唔係隻臭雞<br />\n陳同佳都唔會受人擺佈 比林鄭威逼 以家要做過街老鼠 <br />\n<br />\n點解潘曉穎可以咁殘忍比綠帽佳佳 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e1a35f290aac051dfe9ef49a7b3a708d1675620","tid":1674414,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:57:29.000Z","msg":"咩歌泥？"},{"pid":"a8b50f0c334099d3cfb9668aeffd1cb332d95586","tid":1674414,"uid":1734,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"6e1a35f290aac051dfe9ef49a7b3a708d1675620","tid":1674414,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:57:29.000Z","msg":"咩歌泥？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T07:57:48.000Z","msg":"念念不忘"},{"pid":"a464a66733acc060d0542184bfe8e6239225a525","tid":1674414,"uid":230849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T08:05:41.000Z","msg":"得首富睇少左佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"789365d8d96f249d87c932ea21813c0c842a4282","tid":1674414,"uid":247237,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-25T08:13:02.000Z","msg":"不推文"},{"pid":"f1260838c8a39d4da88d6475cff765d75983aa77","tid":1674414,"uid":431